{"tid":2102237,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聶德權：公務員有集會自由  但不能出席針對政府的集會 ?!","createTime":"2020-07-10T10:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T14:14:15.000Z","uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2533efbc81bdf9da26d8738f8e7b8f689628dc2f","tid":2102237,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">咁即係淨係可以出席收錢嘅集會？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府提出公務員宣誓建議，公務員事務局局長聶德權在立法會一個委員會表示，公務員參加反政府集會及示威，有違誓言。勞聯潘兆平問到，公務員在工餘時間參與政治集會及遊行，以及接受訪問批評政府，會否違反誓言。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權表示，《基本法》及香港有關法例保障港人言論、集會及示威自由，但前提需要守法；而作為公務員，表達意見及參與集會時，<strong>需要清楚知道其行為及言行不能與公務員身分產生衝突，令人覺得與政府對着幹，做法不能接受。</strong>他指，公務員政治中立是指支持在任的行政長官及特區政府，落實政府政策，<strong>如果參與反政府集會、示威，「肯定是違反」。</strong>"},{"pid":"af51b2a37e08723703b7b3bf29d2f43d9533931e","tid":2102237,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:30:17.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>希望大家聽日之前，可以睇一睇呢條片，豐富一下對嚟緊幾個月可能出現嘅選舉操控嘅想像：</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0ggBftnYDQ4&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwuml6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=5d887d2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0ggBftnYDQ4</a>"},{"pid":"ffca3d58c6e2d188652f7f2f6e8d65b3c92061e4","tid":2102237,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537024-20200710.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537024-20200710.htm&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwuml6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=f64e39b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537024-20200710.htm&h=05ecc1b7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537024-20200710.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5927d2ad8f0f4b17045cf6293e0be9f290ce747d","tid":2102237,"uid":170249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:33:33.000Z","msg":"俾言論自由你 但唔準你講阿爺壞話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0f94302ebd8c702275786e19452e7fb98a373e","tid":2102237,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:35:35.000Z","msg":"咁以後公務員人工減到深圳市水平都無得反抗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/03153042/image1591169425245.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2F03153042%2Fimage1591169425245.png&h=7a0449c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望呢位曾經違反公務員誓言意圖顛覆国家政權嘅公務員從速到就近国安公署自首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf79b484dc4efabc83052f692c2a41f595c68ea1","tid":2102237,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2533efbc81bdf9da26d8738f8e7b8f689628dc2f","tid":2102237,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T10:28:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">咁即係淨係可以出席收錢嘅集會？</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府提出公務員宣誓建議，公務員事務局局長聶德權在立法會一個委員會表示，公務員參加反政府集會及示威，有違誓言。勞聯潘兆平問到，公務員在工餘時間參與政治集會及遊行，以及接受訪問批評政府，會否違反誓言。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權表示，《基本法》及香港有關法例保障港人言論、集會及示威自由，但前提需要守法；而作為公務員，表達意見及參與集會時，<strong>需要清楚知道其行為及言行不能與公務員身分產生衝突，令人覺得與政府對着幹，做法不能接受。</strong>他指，公務員政治中立是指支持在任的行政長官及特區政府，落實政府政策，<strong>如果參與反政府集會、示威，「肯定是違反」。</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T14:14:15.000Z","msg":"冇權利邊有責任冇責任邊有權利 <br />\n公餘既無權力執行公務 又有咩效忠特首責任 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0SjoTZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0SjoTZ.png&h=8efe9a4a&s={SIZE}\" /> 局長只係制定政策 公務員有公務員敍用委會會監督"}]}